<h4 id="utilizing-vertical-space--shelving-and-wall-units">Utilizing Vertical Space:  Shelving and Wall Units</h4>

<p>Utilize vertical space by installing shelving units and wall-mounted cabinets.  This maximizes storage capacity without taking up valuable floor space.  This is particularly useful in smaller homes or apartments.</p>

